      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>sliced onion</strong> to a small bowl and squeeze the<strong> </strong>juice<strong> </strong>of <strong>half</strong> the<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>lime half[ves] </strong>over</p><p>Add a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>sugar</strong>, then place the <strong>squeezed lime half[ves]</strong> on top for added pickling – this is your<strong> lime</strong> <strong>quick-pickled onion</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
