    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top, tail and peel your <strong>mango[es]</strong></p><p>Stand the <strong>mango[es]</strong> upright and very carefully slice the flesh away from the stone</p><p>Tip: If you feel resistance against your knife, it means you are hitting the stone</p><p>Dice the <strong>mango flesh</strong> roughly, discarding the stone[s]</p>",
