    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the<strong> diced mango </strong>and <strong>green chilli sauce </strong>in a bowl – this is your <strong>green mango salsa</strong></p><p>When the vegetables are almost ready, add your <strong>seeded tortillas</strong> to a baking tray</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 2-3 min or until they're warmed through (alternatively, add them to a plate and microwave for 20 secs on high!)</p>",
