    {
      "instruction": "<p>Divide your<strong> mayo</strong> equally between the <strong>seeded tortillas</strong> with the <strong>berbere vegetables</strong></p><p>Top with the <strong>green mango salsa</strong> and any <strong>remaining green chilli sauce </strong>– these are your <strong>berbere sweet potato tacos with green mango salsa</strong></p><p>Sprinkle over the <strong>lime quick-pickled onions</strong> and garnish with the <strong>reserved coriander leaves</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
